,"lang_name":"Kube"},{"language":"tk","lang_name":"Turkmen"},{"language":"eo","lang_name":"Esperanto"},{"language":"kiw","lang_name":"Kiwai"}]},{"phelps":"BH10505","text":"DA-MEH UPEH, DA-MEH UPEH,\nSEMES DA-NEH-MEH-NEH HA BEYUH MEH, DEAS MA-DE-ZA-POING DA BE-YAH NA-HA-NEE-DOH SOO- WI-KH DA-MEH UPEH DE-NEE TA GWAP DEAS DA DE-NEE-TA-GWAP KOOPH NAHK. MA DE DE-MA-ZI, UPEH, SU-KA MA-DEH HA-NEE DOH, DEAS GU-TA MA DEH M-EH SOO-NEEK SEE-DEH U-MA-BEE-ZA-KHON-DOH. DAMEH UPEH. GA DEAS MA-DEH ZA-PEH-TINDH, MA-DEH-DAH-TI-GEEK, MA-DEH NA-SOO BA-DU KHAN DOH, SOO-KA DA-NA-BOO-IPH. DEAS MA-DEH BE-YUH ZA-NEE-SHOON-GAH, MA-DEH GA-ME-NGH.\n\n* O my God! O my God! Unite the hearts of Thy servants, and reveal to them Thy great purpose. May they follow Thy commandments and abide in Thy law. Help them, O God, in their endeavour, and grant them strength to serve Thee.  O God! Leave them not to themselves, but guide their steps by the light of Thy knowledge, and cheer their hearts by Thy love. Verily, Thou art their helper and their Lord.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"f07ab5d1-280c-42b9-ba79-03f9c4e0d7c5","book_cats":{"af":{"cat":"Vergaderings","order_in_cat":3},"bn":{"cat":"একতার জন্য প্রার্থনা","order_in_cat":1},"cs":{"cat":"Jednota","order_in_cat":1},"da":{"cat":"Enhed","order_in_cat":1},"en":{"cat":"Unity","order_in_cat":1},"et":{"cat":"Ühtsus","order_in_cat":2},"fr":{"cat":"Unité","order_in_cat":2},"gu":{"cat":"એકતા","order_in_cat":2},"hi":{"cat":"एकता","order_in_cat":1},"hr":{"cat":"Jedinstvo","order_in_cat":1},"hy":{"cat":"ՄԻԱՍՆՈՒԹՅՈՒՆ","order_in_cat":1},"is":{"cat":"Eining","order_in_cat":1},"it":{"cat":"Unità","order_in_cat":1},"ja":{"cat":"一致和合","order_in_cat":1},"kl":{"cat":"Ataasiussuseq","order_in_cat":1},"kn":{"cat":"ಐಕ್ಯತೆಗಾಗಿ","order_in_cat":2},"ko":{"cat":"결혼","order_in_cat":2},"lb":{"cat":"Eenheet a Fridden","order_in_cat":1},"lv":{"cat":"Vienotība","order_in_cat":1},"ml":{"cat":"ഐക്യം","order_in_cat":1},"mn":{"cat":"ЭВ НЭГДЭЛ","order_in_cat":2},"ne":{"cat":"एकता